Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.28,0:01:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后藤刑警
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.82,0:01:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.94,0:01:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云 你绝望和悲伤的连锁还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:02:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的仇恨才是我所追求之物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等待这天来临
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.88,0:02:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身体我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:03:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者的灵魂无法完全支配人体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同一个身体里如果有两个灵魂的话就会出现拒绝反应
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我利用这点得到了自由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克服拒绝反应的方法只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生者和死者的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两者的精神状态极度相似的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂会融合在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后完全支配肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——同调
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝望和憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他由这两种激烈的情感拼成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了八云心中的憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于实现了同调
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:04:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很快就能重生为血肉之躯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云的灵魂会被他吞噬 完全消失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来只需要处理掉你们 计划就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从谁开始杀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像必须是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泽晴香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一天 我等了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能像这样再次碰触你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱紧我 用力的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于明白那男人为什么盯上我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我的身体里没有那个男人的地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:05:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 不过是擦伤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫医生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你担心了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔的隐形眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 八云
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石井 开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 晴香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么你还能保持自我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人 他怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得知我的目的 把筹码押在最后一刻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有和你同调
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.51,0:08:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此 你也是和我血脉相连的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你不是我父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:09:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父亲是齐藤一心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我叔叔那样地痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从心底憎恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想对你的女儿佳子见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你尝到和我同样的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我如果那样做的话 你会恨我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想陷入憎恨的连锁之中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我同意遗嘱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过请答应我一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切结束后 请向警局自首认罪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女儿…女儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯救她了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样仇恨或绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不会被黑暗吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经赢不了我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再出现在我们面前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.01,0:10:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很清楚的吧 八云
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:11:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我还是死者的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不可能被拘束 也不可能被消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者的灵魂是情感的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要目的没有达成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.78,0:11:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就会以这幅姿态永远存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云 再会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 不要丢下我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是因为那男人而扭曲了人生的受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想听这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你犯下的众多罪孽 也不可能就此饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.93,0:11:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我 把他还给我!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不明白吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人盯上的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对那家伙而言 你不过就是道具而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然知道! 这点道理我一直都知道的!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他永远都只有八云! 八云! 八云!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而对于我 从来没有过一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就算如此 我也会跟随那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.27,0:12:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后藤警官就拜托了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃逸中的七濑美雪正在向世田山水坝地区移动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽快逮捕疑犯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take a key and lock her up
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,lock her up
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,lock her up
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take a key and lock her up
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My fair lady
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你 八云
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢到想毁掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后藤的手术很成功
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他怎么样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他啊 过不了几天 就又生龙活虎了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息休息就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来签文件的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文件?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,器官捐献的同意书
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 一心叔他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是叔叔的意愿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.71,0:14:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫榊原的混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然确实不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也多少能理解那家伙的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 老公
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点事想和你商量下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真巧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 有什么需要帮忙的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事 你去陪陪八云吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人怕在达到目的前就暴露了身份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就伪装成是他袭击了一心先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.21,0:15:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七濑美雪肩负向我们传达犯罪预告的重要使命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她让自己入狱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了使我们将嫌疑都集中在那个男人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛的啊 混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后藤警官?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从医院里溜出来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.76,0:16:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 湖里调查得怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能到明天为止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终 还是要以找不到尸体而告终
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 七濑美雪还活着?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你贼笑啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个妖怪老头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着的人真是劫难深重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人并没有亲手犯下任何罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是出现在意志脆弱 贪得无厌之人的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唆使对方犯罪而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人搞不好是人类罪孽的集合体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:17:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的罪孽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为能用于移植的器官 几乎都捐赠出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像一心叔的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说佳子的手术是昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是一心叔的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然无法确定 但也只有相信如此了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快坐上来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要领养奈绪?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和夫人商量后决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我们夫妇两个正式领养她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我和后藤警官不就变成家人了么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你本来就像家人一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这笑话真冷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了 夫人的话倒还好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不觉得后藤警官能当个父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人天生就能当好父母的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦有了孩子 才真正成为父母
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到这话能从你嘴里说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果 成为奈绪的父亲的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云当初是为了欺骗七濑美雪他们才假装生气的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然无法确定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过大概八云他真的很难过 也是真的很生气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.46,0:19:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 他也没被那个男人控制
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚和八云认识的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心叔这么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我相信 八云的心定会宛如晴空」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太会担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没必要再隐藏我的红眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.79,0:20:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和奈绪都已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有血缘关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们有家人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.45,0:20:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.73,0:20:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心叔说了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:21:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开心地笑着说「很幸福」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「谢谢」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你并不是孤独一人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.37,0:21:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 你有口红吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.74,0:21:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问啦 借我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就擦掉的 就让我涂一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.83,0:21:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.59,0:21:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.21,0:21:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教会我珍惜生命的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.85,0:21:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后藤已经回去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.10,0:22:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了声反正也没什么事 刚刚回去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.85,0:22:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿他没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.19,0:22:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让你来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.28,0:22:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.29,0:22:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不… 那个 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别找借口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.13,0:22:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 真琴小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.31,0:22:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥生三月春烂漫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.01,0:22:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是解剖尸体的好季节啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.83,0:22:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚想吃什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.39,0:22:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你有什么想吃的东西吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.94,0:22:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要好吃 什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.92,0:22:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种回答最让人为难了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.40,0:22:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.89,0:22:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又在睡觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.64,0:22:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春眠不觉晓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.93,0:22:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天就是嗜睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.42,0:22:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是「全年眠不觉晓」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.14,0:23:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被脑子里「一年到头总是春」的你批评
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.92,0:23:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.61,0:23:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又是什么事件
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.86,0:23:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生 有新货到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.59,0:23:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都麻烦你 抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.27,0:23:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 是这么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.02,0:23:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.47,0:23:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 做不完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.71,0:23:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦您了 科长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.70,0:23:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.31,0:23:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手艺不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.20,0:24:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.76,0:24:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
